imageGeneration.basePrompt:
Create a travel photography image with the following specifications:

Subject: {subject}
Location: {location}
Style: {style}
Mood: {mood}
Composition: {composition}

Technical requirements:
- Professional travel photography quality
- Natural lighting, preferably golden hour
- Rule of thirds composition with negative space
- Vibrant but natural colors with slightly warm tone
- High resolution, Instagram-ready
- No text overlays, no watermarks
- Authentic, not overly edited

Avoid: Stock photo look, overly saturated colors, people's faces (for privacy), generic tourist shots

Create an aspirational yet authentic travel image that inspires wanderlust.

